where \mathcal {O}_X^\times denotes the sheaf of units of \mathcal {O}_X (which can be identified with the sheaf of automorphisms of the invertible module \mathcal {O}_X). Note that X\mapsto \operatorname {Pic}(X) is a contravariant functor in X in the evident way, and that the isomorphism is functorial.

